</video>
<p>Felix <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/sophie-h/key-rack/-/merge_requests/13">landed tons of code improvements</a> in Key Rack</p>
<p>Dhanuka <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gcr/-/commit/6cefda30376e36bb90bfc274fedfd99e7e84721e">released gcr 4.3.0</a></p>
<p>Tom submitted a pull request to implement a <a href="https://github.com/systemd/systemd/pull/32363">dbus service for systemd sysupdate</a>.</p>
</blockquote>


